1. How to add / remove events dynamically without using event attributes (eg:  onclick, ...)

->addEventListener() method attaches an event handler to the specified element
->we can add many event handlers to one element
->we can add many event handlers of the same type to one element,i.e. two "click" events
->we can add event listener to any DOM

2. How to destructuring arrays in JavaScript?

->To destructure an array in JavaScript, we use the square brackets [] to store the variable name which will be assigned to the name of the array storing the element.
->const [var1, var2, ...] = arrayName;